<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039285" n="1"/> <pb facs="1039286" n="2"/>
  <opener><salute><lb/>Viro Reverendo atque Clarissimo
    <lb/>Domino <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Jacobo Hermanno</rs>
    <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolaus Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.
</salute></opener>
  <p><lb/><del/><add>Gratus admodum fuit et l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus quem</add> ex <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118634771">Wolfii</rs> ad <rs type="person" key="">Patruum</rs> <rs type="letters">literis</rs> <del/><add>accepi de</add> <rs type="keyword">vocatione</rs> <del/><add>Tua</add>
    <lb/>ad <rs type="organisation"><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2925535">Francofurtanam</rs> <rs type="organisation">Academiam</rs></rs> <del/>nuntius. Gratulor Tibi impense de honori<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fica ista ad hanc stationem invitatione facta ab ipso <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118535978">Rege</rs> Potentissimo cum singu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lari eruditionis Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dicatione. Faxit Deus, ut novum hoc munus, quod
    <lb/>Te minime detrectarum persuasus sum, cedat in sui gloriam, <rs type="persons">Parentum</rs> Tuorum
    <lb/>Honoratissimorum gaudium, Clarissimi <del/><add>majoremque indies</add> Nominis Tui <del/>celebritatem,
    <lb/><del/><add>faxit etiam</add> ut in futura muneris hujus administratione <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118535978">Regi</rs> Potentissimo, quod non ulti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ma laus erit, placeas! Moveat <del/>quoque novus iste qui ad honores Tuos accedit cumu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lus <rs type="persons">Rectores</rs> <rs type="organisation">Academi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, ut eruditionem Tuam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exteris in tanto
    <lb/>pretio est, digna tandem prosequantur <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimatione, nec eos qui tanta cum
    <lb/>laude <del/><add>jam docent</add> postponant amplius illis, quibus inter discentes
    <lb/>potius locus esse debet. <del/><add>Quod</add> substitutionem meam cum <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavio</rs> discedes apud
    <lb/><rs type="persons">Proceres</rs> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3164603">Venetos</rs> Te promoturum toties jam testatus es, su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>as ago gra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tias, nec est cur Te denuo moneam hac de re quam totam prudenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>itto. <add>Accepi heri <rs type="letter">literas</rs> ab</add> Amplissim<add>o</add> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118571249">Leibniti<add>o</add></rs> <del/><add>in quibus ut et in eis quas ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> dedit promisit se</add>
    <lb/>et co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatione sua <add>pariter</add> mihi adfuturum, adjecitque se <add>de</add> ratione qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ipsi co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dissima videretur negotium hoc exequendi ad Te scripsisse. Arbitratur Vir
    <lb/><del/>Amplissimus <del/><add>quod</add> licet vocationem Regiam acceperis, non ideo minus <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c
    <lb/>propria sunt ejus verba<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> poteris rem tegere <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs>, et moram trahere,
    <lb/>donec terminus expirarit. Quod si vero Tu nihilo minus<del/>
    <lb/><del/>discessum Tuum maturandum censeas, rogo ut id mihi significare ne
    <lb/>dedigneris, quo possim Amplissimo <abbr>Dno</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118571249">Leibnitio</rs> propositum Tuum quam<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>primum notificare illumque precari, ut co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endationem suam urgeat.
    <lb/>Non dubito multos fore <rs type="persons">competitores</rs>, et inter illos etiam <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzagliam</rs>,
    <lb/>sed ipsi, ut <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118571249">Leibnitius</rs> scribit, oberit admissus nuper error et impotens
    <lb/>contra Te acerbitas. Miror sane quod Te tam indignis modis tractave<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rit; su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>am controversi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quam nondum recte scio, si mihi perscribere
    <lb/>velis, rem facies
    <lb/><unclear>gra</unclear>tissimam.</p></div></body>
